
SHADOWS


.shadow-{size}

Sizes


md
lg
xl
2xl


inner
outline
outline
none


Starting with a box:


 <body class="h-screen bg-gray-200 flex justify-center items-center p-6">
        
<div class="bg-blue-900 text-blue-200 w-40 h-40 flex justify-center items-center">
Here is a cool box
</div>
        
</body>

Adding a box shadow to it:

shadow-lg

<div class="shadow-lg bg-blue-900 text-blue-200 w-40 h-40 flex justify-center items-center">


OPACITY  == WHEN You want something to get a disable look.


Percentages

.opacity-{percent}

100
75
50
25
0

Change in the box opacity-50:



<div class="opacity-50 bg-blue-900 text-blue-200 w-40 h-40 flex justify-center items-center">
Here is a cool box
</div>



Change it to 25


--TEST IT---

CURSOR


.cursor-{style}

Styles

default
pointer
wait
text
move
not-allowed

Add a class to the div of: 

cursor-move

Test it

SELECT

Styles

none
text
all
auto


Unable select to the users:

add the select-none class


place it inside the body


 <body class="h-screen bg-gray-200 flex justify-center items-center p-6">
        
<div class="select-none bg-blue-900 text-blue-200 w-40 h-40 flex justify-center items-center">
     Here is a cool box
</div>
        
</body>


It wont let you select

Now, select the entire line with a single click with select-all



 <body class="h-screen bg-gray-200 flex justify-center items-center p-6">
        
<div class="select-all bg-blue-900 text-blue-200 w-40 h-40 flex justify-center items-center">
     Here is a cool box
</div>
        
</body>


